Kmax<-15
wcss<-rep(NA,Kmax)
nClust<- list()
for(i in 1:Kmax){
  fit<-kmeans(df,i)
  wcss[i]<-fit$tot.withinss
  nClust[[i]]<-fit$size
}
plot(1:Kmax,wcss,type="b",pch=19)
